Vidya SAGAR, petitioner,
v.
ORACLE CORPORATION. No. 13-328. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 21, 2013. Case below, 523 Fed.Appx. 999 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied. Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
